{"tid":1420633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家睇下6.7暴動事件反映左d 咩","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:43:10.000Z","uid":296408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e4fbca1747f34a3a5763dbb32adaa4244a2d3e1e","tid":1420633,"uid":296408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"因為上網睇到d 人話6.7 暴動先係真正既暴動, 我上網睇左下d 資料然後發現以下內容:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;「六七暴動」事件落幕後，政府察覺到有需要調整過時的管治策略，例如修改勞工法例、成立民政處、發展本土化、以廣東話取代國語、還有在教育、醫療、廉政、房屋等各方面進行改革。&quot;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暴動期間，最少造成包括 11 名警務人員殉職在內的 52 人死亡，包括 212 名警員在內的802人受傷，1,936 人被檢控；事件中總共涉及 1,167 個炸彈。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">即係話, 要動用到咁多個炸彈, 咁多條人命, 咁多人被檢控, 先<strong>&quot;有可能&quot;</strong>令呢個政府反思現況去進行改變. </span><br />\n<br />\n***永不割蔗***<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dztd8Wm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdztd8Wm.png&h=dc41a27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://photoblog.hk/255367/%e5%be%9e%e7%8f%8d%e8%b2%b4%e8%88%8a%e7%85%a7%e7%89%87%e4%ba%86%e8%a7%a3%ef%bc%8c%e5%b7%a5%e8%81%af%e6%9c%83%e6%8e%a8%e5%8b%95%e7%9a%84%e3%80%8c%e5%85%ad%e4%b8%83%e6%9a%b4%e5%8b%95%e3%80%8d%e6%98%af/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F255367%2F%25e5%25be%259e%25e7%258f%258d%25e8%25b2%25b4%25e8%2588%258a%25e7%2585%25a7%25e7%2589%2587%25e4%25ba%2586%25e8%25a7%25a3%25ef%25bc%258c%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e8%2581%25af%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%258e%25a8%25e5%258b%2595%25e7%259a%2584%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2585%25ad%25e4%25b8%2583%25e6%259a%25b4%25e5%258b%2595%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%2598%25af%2F&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=266721db\" target=\"_blank\">https://photoblog.hk/255367/%e5%be%9e%e7%8f%8d%e8%b2%b4%e8%88%8a%e7%85%a7%e7%89%87%e4%ba%86%e8%a7%a3%ef%bc%8c%e5%b7%a5%e8%81%af%e6%9c%83%e6%8e%a8%e5%8b%